OL,1,D]S737{kkkc5FNorthern Ireland prisons:  
OL,2,D]S555{jjj25F'Solitary confinement'     
OL,3,D]Suuu{rrzq5Fbreaking UN standards      
OL,4,T#######################################
OL,5, Some Northern Ireland prisoners are    
OL,6, being held in what amounts to "solitary
OL,7, confinement" in breach of international
OL,8, standards, a report has found.         
OL,10,FCCTV recordings over a five-day period 
OL,11,Fshowed 20 inmates at Maghaberry Prison 
OL,12,Fnear Lisburn did not leave their cells.
OL,14,FThe report by Criminal Justice         
OL,15,FInspection (CJI) raised "significant   
OL,16,Fconcerns about the treatment of        
OL,17,Fprisoners".                            
OL,19,FThe Prison Service said parts of the   
OL,20,Freport make for difficult reading.     
